*Tenant has separte domain and separate database
--------------------------------------------------

# Phase One: SaaS Admin

Microservice 1: Authentication Service (Identity and access management)
Tables: User, User-Roles, Role-Permissions
Security: JWT


Microservice 2 : User Services
tables: User Account, Role, Permission


Microservice 3: Tenant Service
Tables: Tenant, Location, Division-Type


Microservice 3: Subscription and Payment Service
Tables: Subscription (trail), Plan (standard), Payment


Microservice 5: Messaging Service
Tables: Message, Messages-Permissions


---------------------------------------------------


# Phase Two: Organization Administrator

Micorservice 1: Subscription and Payment Service
Tables: Plan, Subscription, Payment


Microservice 2: User Services
Tables: User Account (dep-admin), add-permissions to roles


Microservice 3: Tenant and Division Management
Tables: Divisions, Tenant-Divisions


Microservice 4: Messaging Service
Tables: Message


Microservice 5: Notifications
Tables: Notification

---------------------------------------------------

